comments: Some characters looked somewhat familiar, and some of the characters were present in all of the words. I tried to associate some characters to something the objects reminded me of. I also was only looking at the third and fifth character in each word, because they were enough to distinguish the different words. The task where I had just a brief moment to see the words and I had to identify the object looked very challenging at first, but I did surprisingly well, compared to how I thought I would do initially.
